        "text_rm4HUW": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<h3><strong>10% Commission + 10% Off for Your Audience</strong></h3><p>Approved affiliates earn <strong>10% commission</strong> on qualifying referred sales, while their audience receives <strong>10% off</strong> through a unique referral link or discount code.</p><h3><strong>Easy Tracking Through Shopify Collabs</strong></h3><p>Every approved affiliate receives a <strong>unique referral link or discount code</strong>. Sales are tracked automatically through Shopify Collabs, and affiliates get access to a dashboard to monitor <strong>clicks, sales, and commissions</strong>.</p><h3><strong>No Minimum Sales Requirement</strong></h3><p>There is <strong>no minimum sales threshold</strong> to start earning. Every eligible sale made through your referral link or code can generate commission based on the agreed terms.</p><h3><strong>Premium Products That Fit the Right Audience</strong></h3><p>AirVape offers sleek, high-quality vaporizers designed for modern consumers who value performance, portability, and design. That makes AirVape easier to promote to audiences that already align with the category.</p>"
          }
        }
      },
